      <text bytes="21549" xml:space="preserve">{{for|the Milanese ruler|Luchino Visconti (died 1349)}}
{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2015}}
{{Infobox person
| image =Luchino Visconti 1972.jpg
| caption = Visconti in 1972
